类 OrFilterFunction<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.cep.pattern.OrFilterFunction<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - Type of the element to filter
    所有已实现的接口:

    已过时。 
    This is only used when migrating from an older Flink version. Use the OrCondition instead.

    @Deprecated
public class OrFilterFunction<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements FilterFunction<T>
    A filter function which combines two filter functions with a logical or. Thus, the filter function only returns true, iff at least one of the filter functions holds true.

      • filter

        public boolean filter(T value)
               throws java.lang.Exception
        已过时。 
        从接口复制的说明: FilterFunction
        The filter function that evaluates the predicate.

        IMPORTANT: The system assumes that the function does not modify the elements on which the predicate is applied. Violating this assumption can lead to incorrect results.

        指定者:
        filter 在接口中 FilterFunction<T>
        参数:
        value - The value to be filtered.
        返回:
        True for values that should be retained, false for values to be filtered out.
        抛出:
        java.lang.Exception - This method may throw exceptions. Throwing an exception will cause the operation to fail and may trigger recovery.
